{"tid":2142147,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食平西好地方　$195歎理大酒管系學生誠意FYP","createTime":"2020-08-06T08:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T15:19:56.000Z","uid":225931,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5122f6084bbe005bbd25dfb20d987addee61af8","tid":2142147,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peo6EFP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpeo6EFP.jpg&h=b6295959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大學生的FYP（畢業作品）會做甚麼？論文？作品集？還是微電影？<br />\n<br />\n你有想過FYP可以經營餐廳嗎？由統籌到煮食都是出自學生手中，理工大學「酒店及旅遊業管理學系」的畢業作品就是要同學當一天餐廳經理。<br />\n<br />\n在香港，<br />\n想在一間幽靜、有氣氛的餐廳吃飯，<br />\n未計酒水加一，<br />\n閒閒地每人300元一餐，<br />\n但在尖東範圍竟有親民價的西餐存在。<br />\n<br />\n在理工大學<br />\n「酒店及旅遊業管理學系」學院底層，<br />\n向下走兩層，<br />\n再經過昏暗的長廊<br />\n就是Bistro 1979，<br />\n不是常客、不是旁邊Hotel ICON的住客，<br />\n都不會知道這餐廳的存在。"},{"pid":"22d9db50758cfe97a7dca0495a3035c2842c7ed0","tid":2142147,"uid":130303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T08:36:00.000Z","msg":"hotel icon係藍，不了"},{"pid":"afd2023624b6adbf83484ed2816c910e41c2fa70","tid":2142147,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"包唔包屌?"},{"pid":"636ef7d7776e3e48c7fd64ae2605d8bb2e9bb6c7","tid":2142147,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T15:19:56.000Z","msg":"咁都可以係fyp 垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}